# Bake & Grill — Full Development Guide

## Project Overview

Restaurant management SaaS for Bake & Grill (Maldives). Monorepo with Laravel backend, 4 React frontends, shared TypeScript package, and a print proxy microservice.

---

## Monorepo Structure

```
/
├── backend/                    # Laravel 11 (PHP 8.2+)
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── Domains/            # 15 DDD bounded contexts
│   │   ├── Http/Controllers/   # Thin controllers (API + web)
│   │   ├── Models/             # 77 Eloquent models
│   │   ├── Traits/             # HasPermissions, etc.
│   │   ├── Providers/          # App, Auth, DomainEvent service providers
│   │   └── Services/           # Legacy (prefer Domains/)
│   ├── routes/
│   │   ├── api.php             # ~160+ admin API endpoints
│   │   ├── api_finance.php     # Finance sub-routes
│   │   └── web.php             # Customer portal, receipts
│   ├── database/
│   │   └── seeders/PermissionSeeder.php  # 48 permissions, 3 roles
│   └── config/services.php     # Third-party credentials
├── apps/
│   ├── admin-dashboard/        # Admin panel (React/TS, Vite)
│   ├── pos-web/                # Point of Sale terminal
