## Payment Gateway Architecture

Located in `backend/app/Domains/Payments/Gateway/`.

- Stripe integration with webhook handling
- Payment state machine manages lifecycle: pending → processing → completed/failed/refunded
- Events: `PaymentCompleted`, `PaymentFailed`, `RefundProcessed`

